# Deploy on Code Change

After making any code changes to this project:

1. **Commit** the changes with a clear, descriptive message
2. **Push** to the `mvf` remote (`git push mvf main`)

This triggers automatic deployment to https://solar-form-eight.vercel.app via Vercel's Git integration (MVF Projects Pro team).

Exclude untracked/draft files (e.g. `chameleon/`) unless explicitly requested.
